Scorponok


Scorponok looked at Darkmouse's Brain. He slowly Checked to make sure 
she knew of Megatron and megatron being the Leadar. He made sure She 
knew that QuickStrike was 2nd in command. He also made a list of all 
the other bots in their little group in her head. Scorponok then
pulls 
out a little laptop and plugs it into Darkmouse's Processing unit.
She 
pulls out, from the laptop, two little blocks with a button on it. He 
hids the laptop and the 2 blocks. He slowly wakes up Darkmouse. "All 
finish." Scorponok walks away with the laptop and the two blocks. He 
puts the laptop and 1 of the blocks in his hand. He takes the other 
block and walks up too Megatron. "I have a present for you Megatron."
